name: Roquelaire
body:
### Thank you!

Roquelaire is discontinued. I want to thank you all for your support and interest, but I can no longer devote the time necessary to keep Roquelaire functional.

If you have any questions or concerns, I can be contacted [via reddit](http://www.reddit.com/message/compose/?to=Kamoi).

-Kamoi
